Review Text: The dosas are really good over here. It's crisp and tastes fresh. Chutney has proper consistency. Sambar could have been better. Value for money
Ordered dosas from this place many times. Love them. They serve it with Sambhar and coconut chutney with good quantity. Pocket friendly prices and quick delivery.
Ordered puri and upma dosa, delivered 2 masala dosa. Taste was okay but quality is not good.
two uttapam is over roasted and it is unable to eat
the masal utappam is not correctly boiled.
in mashala dhosa thr is no mashala
got no curry for  puri.... upmadosa is not good

Timely delivery via Ubereats..
Masala dosa not worth the price 35/- quality and quantity wise....I get an excellent masala dosa @25-30/- with bigger size and generous stuffing of masala, onions etc....Masala doesn't mean only mashed boiled potato inside.
The tiffins are not at all good there is no salt in chutneys even in dosa waste of money.
Chuntey was not a good. And puri is also not good
